caption: The image is an advertisement for a haunted house event taking place on October 31st, 2021. The event is being held at 123 Anywhere St., Any City, ST 12345. Tickets are available for $25, and the advertisement encourages attendees to "face your fears!" The website for the event is www.reallygreatsite.com.
